{"tid":2190681,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"曲解口罩令 警阻人公園開餐","createTime":"2020-09-06T01:35:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-06T19:56:18.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c4d598af16f404e9a788b69cfdf620411339a3be","tid":2190681,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T01:35:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200906/J3AVPNDBCNBL3BRYUJ6WZPAYZA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200906%2FJ3AVPNDBCNBL3BRYUJ6WZPAYZA%2F&d=bvaV6%2BUCrkGuzNdoarVmR38q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=3e090d0c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200906%2FJ3AVPNDBCNBL3BRYUJ6WZPAYZA%2F&h=35ee05b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200906/J3AVPNDBCNBL3BRYUJ6WZPAYZA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n曲解口罩令 警阻人公園開餐<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】香港警察胡亂執法，各項抗疫法令成為政權滋擾良民的毒藥。一名男子昨在油麻地一個公園因進食而除下口罩，卻被三名警察圍攻警告須戴回，否則發出告票。事主促警解釋法例不得要領。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：在囚男子染疫 港首宗  荔枝角收押所及小欖700人需驗武肺<br />\n<br />\n《預防及控制疾病（佩戴口罩）規例》提供若干情況作為不佩戴口罩的合理辯解，包括飲食。但讀者程小姐（化名）提供短片，顯示警方未有熟讀法例。事發昨晚6時許，她在砵蘭街文明里休憩處休息時，一名男子正在該處用膳，身旁有外賣盒及兩支啤酒。多名警員突上前勸他戴口罩，該男子回應：「我食緊嘢，點解要戴返口罩？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/bfQKmMlBkNE76iFJo_6e_41FXHk=/668x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PFCE6HNF4BB6ZFDKNMVCF6P6FM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FbfQKmMlBkNE76iFJo_6e_41FXHk%3D%2F668x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPFCE6HNF4BB6ZFDKNMVCF6P6FM.jpg&h=0663fd54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■公園男開餐期間遭數名警員喝令戴上口罩。讀者提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要求釐清法例不果<br />\n<br />\n過程中，「佢不斷問警員𠵱家係咪喺公園食嘢係唔得嘅？」警員回應：「係呀！𠵱家我係話唔食得嘢！」一名女警越說越激動，喝令男子「你戴返口罩先好同我講嘢呀！」男子則要求警員站遠一點，「我驚你有病毒」。男子進一步要求警員釐清法例限制是否包括進食，警員回應：「唔可以除口罩呀個法例！喺街就唔可以！」<br />\n<br />\n程小姐指警員一。。。。。"},{"pid":"ba5e3253d58430fb6a3010f4960c93fddd4e78fd","tid":2190681,"uid":36238,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T01:39:06.000Z","msg":"同毅進仔講法律<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嗰班友都唔識睇字"},{"pid":"ed592752537f9a4209928769430b27a2d3ddb0f3","tid":2190681,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T01:40:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d3b8bc8241eaa30e9278ccfeb0ffc7f57dd8035","tid":2190681,"uid":123774,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T01:41:05.000Z","msg":"蝗軍 係咁撚唔專業<br />\n法例?! 佢哋習慣口頭釋法嘛"},{"pid":"87d720789221dd8cc97c0d975e80e4811d77e556","tid":2190681,"uid":277888,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T01:41:24.000Z","msg":"有腦就唔會做狗喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8bee61f08b3f881890a73632aa8f673912013e9","tid":2190681,"uid":11291,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T01:43:56.000Z","msg":"死黑警有警署餐廳<br />\n就算出街做嘢都可以喺警車到食飯<br />\n<br />\n點會知星斗市民嘅痛苦有時要迫住喺公園食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再者黑警淨係識推車推大肚婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71b3b77c111e7b731642871d83b5